text: Olivia Eliasson in 2018 Olivia Margareta Eliasson (born 7 June 1996) is a Swedish singer. Eliasson was discovered when she did a cover of the song "Begging" by singer Anton Ewald and posted it on YouTube. Ewald contacted her after watching the video and they did a duet of the song "Human" together. Olivia Eliasson competed in Melodifestivalen 2018 with the song ”Never Learn”.
